commit_message:
align_and_pad_cell() returns list instead of str.

It's inefficient having align_and_pad_cell() join the list of lines it
generates internally back into a string, only to have that string split
up elsewhere in the code. Keeping it a list here. It'll pay off once I'm
done refactoring the rest of the project.

author: Robpol86
commit_message:
Slightly optimize max_dimensions().

1. Eliminate append to splitlines() list result.
2. Eliminate two calls to max() for widths.
3. Eliminate bug beause len() was used instead of only visible_width().

New fastest time: 10000 loops, best of 3: 72.2 usec per loop
Old fastest time: 10000 loops, best of 3: 73.6 usec per loop

No real difference but I did fix that bug :P
